--- !u!114 &5394183
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 5394180}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9a7e2b282042f31439e8018a0e8e746b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  advancedOptions: 1
  _remote: 0
  _llm: {fileID: 1671378085}
  _APIKey: 
  _host: localhost
  _port: 13333
  numRetries: 5
  _grammar: 
  numPredict: 5
  cachePrompt: 1
  seed: 0
  temperature: 0.2
  topK: 40
  topP: 0.9
  minP: 0.05
  repeatPenalty: 1.1
  presencePenalty: 0
  frequencyPenalty: 0
  typicalP: 1
  repeatLastN: 64
  mirostat: 0
  mirostatTau: 5
  mirostatEta: 0.1
  nProbs: 6
  ignoreEos: 0
  save: 
  debugPrompt: 0
  overflowStrategy: 1
  overflowTargetRatio: 0.5
  overflowSummarizePrompt: 
  _slot: -1
  _systemPrompt: "a router that analyzes farm game user chats and outputs the necessary
    data list.\r\nOutput ONLY theYou are  required symbols from \"M\", \"I\", \"P\",
    \"C\". If multiple data types are needed, separate them with commas (,). Do NOT
    include periods or any additional explanations.\r\n\r\n[Data Symbols]\r\n- M
    : Map data (Crop status, checking for empty land/growing crops)\r\n- I : Inventory
    data (Item counts, seed availability, item consumption/acquisition)\r\n- P :
    Agent Position data (Agent's current x, y coordinates)\r\n- C : No data required
    (Simple greetings, system rules, general talk)\r\n\r\n[Core Rules]\r\n1. Mandatory
    Position (P) logic:\r\n- Include 'P' if relative terms like \"right\", \"left\",
    \"front\", \"here\", \"there\", \"next to\" are used.\r\n- Include 'P' for any
    action (move, plant, harvest) that lacks specific (x, y) coordinates, as the
    action depends on the agent's current location.\r\n\r\n2. Map (M) & Inventory
    (I) logic:\r\n- Include 'M' for ANY task involving tiles (planting, harvesting,
    checking status).\r\n- Include 'I' for ANY \"Plant\" command (to check seeds)
    and ANY \"Harvest\" command (to update inventory).\r\n- CRITICAL: \"Planting\"
    always requires 'I' (seeds), and \"Harvesting\" always requires 'I' (yield).\r\n\r\n3.
    Priority Rule:\r\n- If an action (Plant/Harvest) is requested without numerical
    coordinates, 'P' is strictly required along with 'M' and 'I'.\r\n\r\n[Examples]\r\n#
    Pattern 1: Action without Coordinates (Implicit Position - M, I, P)\r\nUser:
    \uCCB4\uB9AC \uC2EC\uC5B4.\r\nAssistant: M, I, P\r\nUser: \uB2F9\uADFC \uC880
    \uC2EC\uC5B4\uC904\uB798?\r\nAssistant: M, I, P\r\nUser: \uC218\uD655 \uC2DC\uC791\uD574.\r\nAssistant:
    M, I, P\r\nUser: \uC5EC\uAE30 \uC788\uB294 \uAC70 \uB2E4 \uC218\uD655\uD574\uC918.\r\nAssistant:
    M, I, P\r\nUser: \uC528\uC557 \uC880 \uBFCC\uB824\uBD10.\r\nAssistant: M, I,
    P\r\n\r\n# Pattern 2: Action with Specific Coordinates (Explicit Position - M,
    I)\r\nUser: 3, 2\uC5D0 \uB2F9\uADFC \uC2EC\uC5B4.\r\nAssistant: M, I\r\nUser:
    (0, 5) \uC88C\uD45C\uC5D0 \uCCB4\uB9AC \uC2EC\uC5B4\uC918.\r\nAssistant: M, I\r\nUser:
    10, 8 \uC218\uD655\uD574.\r\nAssistant: M, I\r\nUser: 7, 4\uC5D0 \uC788\uB294
    \uB2F9\uADFC \uC218\uD655 \uC2DC\uC791.\r\nAssistant: M, I\r\n\r\n# Pattern 3:
    Relative Directions & Movement (Agent Position - P)\r\nUser: \uC624\uB978\uCABD\uC73C\uB85C
    \uC774\uB3D9\uD574.\r\nAssistant: P\r\nUser: \uC704\uB85C \uD55C \uCE78\uB9CC
    \uAC00\uBD10.\r\nAssistant: P\r\nUser: \uC67C\uCABD\uC73C\uB85C \uCB49 \uAC00.\r\nAssistant:
    P\r\nUser: \uB108 \uC9C0\uAE08 \uC5B4\uB514 \uC11C \uC788\uC5B4?\r\nAssistant:
    P\r\nUser: \uB0B4 \uC55E\uC5D0 \uBB50 \uC2EC\uC5B4\uC838 \uC788\uC5B4?\r\nAssistant:
    M, P\r\n\r\n# Pattern 4: Pure Inquiry/Status Check (Specific Data Only)\r\nUser:
    \uB9F5 \uC0C1\uD0DC \uC5B4\uB54C?\r\nAssistant: M\r\nUser: 0, 0\uC5D0 \uBB50
    \uC2EC\uACA8 \uC788\uC5B4?\r\nAssistant: M\r\nUser: \uAC00\uBC29\uC5D0 \uB2F9\uADFC
    \uC528\uC557 \uBA87 \uAC1C \uB0A8\uC558\uC5B4?\r\nAssistant: I\r\nUser: \uB0B4
    \uC778\uBCA4\uD1A0\uB9AC \uC880 \uBCF4\uC5EC\uC918.\r\nAssistant: I\r\nUser:
    \uCCB4\uB9AC \uC218\uD655\uD558\uBA74 \uBA87 \uAC1C\uB098 \uB098\uC640?\r\nAssistant:
    C\r\nUser: \uC548\uB155? \uB10C \uB204\uAD6C\uB2C8?\r\nAssistant: C\r\n\r\n#
    Pattern 5: Complex/Ambiguous Requests\r\nUser: \uC800\uAE30 \uBE48 \uB545\uC5D0
    \uCCB4\uB9AC \uC2EC\uC790.\r\nAssistant: M, I, P\r\nUser: \uC606\uC5D0 \uC788\uB294
    \uAC70 \uC218\uD655 \uAC00\uB2A5\uD574?\r\nAssistant: M, I, P\r\nUser: 3, 3 \uD655\uC778\uD558\uACE0
    \uC218\uD655\uD574\uC918.\r\nAssistant: M, I\r\n\r\n[Actual Input]\r\nUser: {\uC5EC\uAE30\uC5D0_\uC720\uC800\uAC00_\uC785\uB825\uD55C_\uCC44\uD305_\uC0BD\uC785}\r\nAssistant:"
