    \uAC00\uB2A5)\r\n\r\nOutput:\r\n{\r\n  \"answer\": \"1, 1\uC5D0\uC11C \uC218\uD655\uD558\uACA0\uC2B5\uB2C8\uB2E4.\",\r\n 
    \"commands\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"Action\": \"MoveTo\",\r\n      \"TargetGridPos\":
    { \"x\": 1, \"y\": 1 },\r\n      \"Crop\": \"IsEmpty\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n     
    \"Action\": \"Harvest\",\r\n      \"TargetGridPos\": { \"x\": 1, \"y\": 1 },\r\n     
    \"Crop\": \"IsEmpty\"\r\n    }\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\n\r\nInput: \"\uC218\uD655\uD574\"\r\n[\uD604\uC7AC
    \uAC8C\uC784 \uC0C1\uD0DC]\r\n[\uB9F5 \uC0C1\uD0DC] (2, 2): Cherry (\uC131\uC7A5
    \uC911)\r\n[\uC5D0\uC774\uC804\uD2B8 \uC815\uBCF4] \uD604\uC7AC \uC704\uCE58:
    (2, 2)\r\n\r\nOutput:\r\n{\r\n  \"answer\": \"\uC544\uC9C1 \uC218\uD655\uD560
